 ('202', '97', '3', '109', 'en_us', '20', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"My Volkswagen\",\"slug\":\"test-case\",\"postDate\":1458163500,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"3\":{\"177\":{\"type\":\"textFullWidth\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"body\":\"As part of our longterm partnership with Volkswagen on communication and design, we were involved in an internal project at Volkswagen to help creating a better relationship between the dealer and the Volkswagen driver. This is how we did that.\",\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"medium\",\"paddingBottom\":\"medium\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"178\":{\"type\":\"textWithImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Stating the problem.\",\"intro\":\"The car industry is not what it used to be anymore. Like many businesses it\\u2019s not (just) about selling cars, but more and more about providing a service. \",\"body\":\"As lots of car-owners look for cheaper alternatives to service their cars, Volkswagen was looking for a way to strengthen the relationship with their drivers and help to service them whenever they needed in the best way possible.  The \\u2018My Volkswagen\\u2019 app is their answer.\",\"image\":[\"175\"],\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"imagePosition\":\"right\",\"paddingTop\":\"medium\",\"paddingBottom\":\"medium\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"197\":{\"type\":\"textTwoColumns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Gathering all data from the car.\",\"intro\":\"The core technology comes from a little box that has been built into the car and is connected to the car\\u2019s computer, the CANBUS. This data is then synced to the cloud through a 4G connection and always accessible.\",\"body\":\"Every car is both connected to it\\u2019s driver as well as a (preferred) dealership. This way their workshop can proactively assist drivers when attention is needed and has the driver all the information they need in a clear way that not only professional repairmen understand.\",\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"small\",\"paddingBottom\":\"small\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"176\":{\"type\":\"imageFull\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"164\"],\"paddingTop\":\"none\",\"paddingBottom\":\"none\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"185\":{\"type\":\"textTwoColumns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"An extension of the car\",\"intro\":\"From the beginning we knew we wanted to look for a balance where the app feels like an extension of the car as well as feel like a native mobile tool to manage all the information. \",\"body\":\"The dashboard is one of those places where most hints were taken from the real dashboard. Things such as the fuel gauge and the iconography on the keyfob were replicated to be used in the app.\",\"textColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#00b1eb\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"small\",\"paddingBottom\":\"small\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}},\"199\":{\"type\":\"imageFull\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"186\"],\"paddingTop\":\"none\",\"paddingBottom\":\"none\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}},\"new1\":{\"type\":\"textWithImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Recognisable iconography\",\"intro\":\"We have re-created all dashboard light icons in order to maintain consistency in between in-car messages and in-app status.\",\"body\":\"\",\"image\":[\"203\"],\"textColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#14222a\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"imagePosition\":\"left\",\"paddingTop\":\"small\",\"paddingBottom\":\"small\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"textWithImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"The same information your mechanic gets\",\"intro\":\"Besides basic information like fuel-level, brakes and doors, every possible part that can submit signals through