our car\\u2019s computer is featured in the My Car section.\",\"body\":\"\",\"image\":[\"209\"],\"textColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"imagePosition\":\"right\",\"paddingTop\":\"small\",\"paddingBottom\":\"small\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}},\"214\":{\"type\":\"textWithImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Three levels of warning signs.\",\"intro\":\"The app supports three statuslevels of a specific part. Good, warning and error. Depending on the level, the app gives you instructions on what to do next.\",\"body\":\"\",\"image\":[\"212\"],\"textColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#14222a\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"imagePosition\":\"left\",\"paddingTop\":\"small\",\"paddingBottom\":\"none\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}},\"216\":{\"type\":\"textTwoColumns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Monitoring your style of driving\",\"intro\":\"Think Blue is Volkswagen\\u2019s subbrand of responsible driving with care for the environment. With all data we can pull from your car, we can make a very accurate profile of your driving style. Your Think Blue score.\",\"body\":\"Based on this profile the app provides you with feedback on your driving and overall statistics on fuel consumption and progress in your style.\",\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#f0f5f8\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"medium\",\"paddingBottom\":\"small\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"217\":{\"type\":\"imageFull\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"218\"],\"paddingTop\":\"none\",\"paddingBottom\":\"none\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"new1\":{\"type\":\"textTwoColumns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Keeping track of every drive you make\",\"intro\":\"Whenever you start driving, your trip is being automatically logged. Serving you with an overview of every trip you\\u2019ve made with your car.\",\"body\":\"With every trip that\\u2019s being logged, we register the start and end location, as well as the duration, fuel consumption, average speed and your ThinkBlue score. Besides that we\\u2019ll also allow drivers to mark a drive as commute, private or business for their administration.\",\"textColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#00b1eb\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"small\",\"paddingBottom\":\"none\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"imageFull\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"219\"],\"paddingTop\":\"none\",\"paddingBottom\":\"none\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}}},\"41\":\"Volkswagen\",\"31\":{\"170\":{\"type\":\"item\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Development\",\"contributorName\":\"Sioux\"}}},\"40\":[\"161\"],\"75\":\"Download the app\",\"76\":\"\",\"50\":[\"162\"],\"39\":\"Control your car from the palm of your hand\",\"36\":\"\",\"83\":[\"163\"],\"43\":\"Mobile app\",\"34\":{\"171\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Concept\"}},\"172\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"UX Design\"}},\"173\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Art Direction\"}},\"174\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Visual Design\"}}}}}', '2016-04-06 15:54:53', '2016-04-06 15:54:53', 'ae157b57-d654-4085-9537-561e38938ff3'),
