 ('332', '117', '3', '109', 'en_us', '36', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"109\",\"title\":\"KLM Layover with a Local\",\"slug\":\"layover-with-a-local\",\"postDate\":1458311040,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"3\":{\"130\":{\"type\":\"textFullWidth\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"body\":\"Layover with a Local offers KLM travelers with a stop of 6 hours or more at Amsterdam Schiphol Airport the opportunity to turn this transfer into a trip. \",\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"big\",\"paddingBottom\":\"big\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"132\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"coverImage\":[\"131\"],\"vimeoId\":\"123456\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"none\",\"paddingBottom\":\"small\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"134\":{\"type\":\"textWithImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"70% of travelers have a layover in Amsterdam\",\"intro\":\"With Amsterdam Central Station just 15 minutes away, why not make use of it? Adventure is just around the corner. \",\"body\":\"By connecting travelers to locals we turn waiting time into wander time, and for KLM it\\u2019s just another way to take you somewhere.\",\"image\":[\"362\"],\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"imagePosition\":\"left\",\"paddingTop\":\"big\",\"paddingBottom\":\"small\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}},\"136\":{\"type\":\"textWithImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Intelligent matchmaking based on interests\",\"intro\":\"The element of matching up passengers with locals through a social profile can give hesitation. \",\"body\":\"Therefore, the app uses intelligent matchmaking based on interests, shared languages and availability. Once the traveler requests a meetup, we select 3 locals and notify them with a push notification. \",\"image\":[\"135\"],\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"imagePosition\":\"right\",\"paddingTop\":\"big\",\"paddingBottom\":\"big\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"137\":{\"type\":\"textTwoColumns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"A personal layover guide for travelers\",\"intro\":\"Leaving the airport during a layover is potentially stressful. That\\u2019s why we created a personal layover guide that gives the traveler step-by-step directions.\",\"body\":\"The layover guide is made up from dynamic cards that offer relevant actions at the appropiate times. Real-time notifications ensure that the traveler returns to the airport in time.\",\"textColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#00a1de\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"big\",\"paddingBottom\":\"small\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}},\"new1\":{\"type\":\"imageFull\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"363\"],\"paddingTop\":\"none\",\"paddingBottom\":\"none\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}},\"143\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"coverImage\":[\"131\"],\"vimeoId\":\"123456\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"big\",\"paddingBottom\":\"big\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"145\":{\"type\":\"textWithImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"An all-inclusive mini trip\",\"intro\":\"In collaboration with the national railway company we offer the traveler a free train ticket into the city.\",\"body\":\"But there is more. At selected bars, they can get their first drink for free, available through an in-app coupon. As a local, you can set your availability so you can meet up with travelers only when you really want to.\",\"image\":[\"364\"],\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"imagePosition\":\"right\",\"paddingTop\":\"small\",\"paddingBottom\":\"small\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"147\":{\"type\":\"textTwoColumns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"So, how do we get the locals to sign up?\",\"intro