 drivers when attention is needed and has the driver all the information they need in a clear way that not only professional repairmen understand.\",\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"small\",\"paddingBottom\":\"small\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"176\":{\"type\":\"imageFull\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"164\"],\"paddingTop\":\"none\",\"paddingBottom\":\"none\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"185\":{\"type\":\"textTwoColumns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"An extension of the car\",\"intro\":\"From the beginning we knew we wanted to look for a balance where the app feels like an extension of the car as well as feel like a native mobile tool to manage all the information. \",\"body\":\"The dashboard is one of those places where most hints were taken from the real dashboard. Things such as the fuel gauge and the iconography on the keyfob were replicated to be used in the app.\",\"textColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#00b1eb\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"small\",\"paddingBottom\":\"small\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}},\"199\":{\"type\":\"imageFull\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"186\"],\"paddingTop\":\"none\",\"paddingBottom\":\"none\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}},\"210\":{\"type\":\"textWithImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Recognisable iconography\",\"intro\":\"We have re-created all dashboard light icons in order to maintain consistency in between in-car messages and in-app status.\",\"body\":\"\",\"image\":[\"203\"],\"textColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#14222a\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"imagePosition\":\"left\",\"paddingTop\":\"small\",\"paddingBottom\":\"small\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}},\"211\":{\"type\":\"textWithImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"The same information your mechanic gets\",\"intro\":\"Besides basic information like fuel-level, brakes and doors, every possible part that can submit signals through your car\\u2019s computer is featured in the My Car section.\",\"body\":\"\",\"image\":[\"209\"],\"textColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#14222a\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"imagePosition\":\"right\",\"paddingTop\":\"small\",\"paddingBottom\":\"small\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}},\"214\":{\"type\":\"textWithImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Three levels of warning signs.\",\"intro\":\"The app supports three statuslevels of a specific part. Good, warning and error. Depending on the level, the app gives you instructions on what to do next.\",\"body\":\"\",\"image\":[\"212\"],\"textColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#14222a\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"imagePosition\":\"left\",\"paddingTop\":\"small\",\"paddingBottom\":\"none\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}},\"216\":{\"type\":\"textTwoColumns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Monitoring your style of driving\",\"intro\":\"Think Blue is Volkswagen\\u2019s subbrand of responsible driving with care for the environment. With all data we can pull from your car, we can make a very accurate profile of your driving style. Your Think Blue score.\",\"body\":\"Based on this profile the app provides you with feedback on your driving and overall statistics on fuel consumption and progress in your style.\",\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#f0f5f8\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"medium\",\"paddingBottom\":\"small\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"440\":{\"type\":\"largeImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"438\"],\"backgroundColor\":\"#1cb2ec\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"439\"],\"paddingTop\":\"medium\",\"paddingBottom\":\"medium\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"220\":{\"type\":\"textTwoColumns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Keeping track of every drive you make\",\"intro\":\"Whenever you start driving, your trip is being automatically logged. Serving you with an overview of every trip you\\u2019ve made with your car.\",\"body\":\"With every trip that\\u2019s being logged, we register the start and end location, as well as the duration, fuel consumption, average speed and your ThinkBlue score. Besides that we\\u2019ll also allow drivers to mark a drive as commute, private or business for their administration.\",\"textColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#00b1eb\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"small\",\"paddingBottom\":\"none\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}},\"442\":{\"type\":\"largeImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"441\"],\"backgroundColor\":\"#1cb2ec\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"small\",\"paddingBottom\":\"medium\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"225\":{\"type\":\"textWithImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Dude, where\'s my car?\",\"intro\":\"No more searching for your car in an overcrowded parking lot with the car locator. \",\"body\":\"The car locator also comes with a movement alert. The app will notify you when your car starts moving, either because it\\u2019s being stolen, towed or when your son-in-law decides to take a joyride. \",\"image\":[\"222\"],\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#f0f5f8\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"imagePosition\":\"right\",\"paddingTop\":\"medium\",\"paddingBottom\":\"small\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"226\":{\"type\":\"textWithImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Houston, we have a problem\",\"intro\":\"And whenever you may find yourself stuck alongside the road due to a breakdown, Volkswagen will come and get you. And because you\\u2019re using the app, they know exactly where you are and what\\u2019s wrong.\",\"body\":\"\",\"image\":[\"223\"],\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#f0f5f8\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"imagePosition\":\"left\",\"paddingTop\":\"none\",\"paddingBottom\":\"medium\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}}},\"41\":\"Volkswagen\",\"31\":{\"170\":{\"type\":\"item\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Development\",\"contributorName\":\"Sioux\"}}},\"40\":[\"161\"],\"75\":\"Download the app\",\"76\":\"\",\"50\":[\"435\"],\"39\":\"Control your car from the palm of your hand\",\"36\":\"\",\"83\":[\"436\"],\"43\":\"Mobile app\",\"34\":{\"171\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Concept\"}},\"172\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"UX Design\"}},\"173\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Art Direction\"}},\"174\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Visual Design\"}}}}}', '2016-04-13 16:56:16', '2016-04-13 16:56:16', '40064326-e18c-42ae-9fa0-2a575134a6af'),
