ce their italian with a real italian. \",\"body\":\"In collaboration with language schools, the expat centre and local bars we make sure to find locals that are excited for a meetup. One lucky local will win a ticket to the country of the traveler.\",\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"medium\",\"paddingBottom\":\"medium\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"148\":{\"type\":\"largeImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"146\"],\"backgroundColor\":\"#cae3ed\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"medium\",\"paddingBottom\":\"medium\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"369\":{\"type\":\"largeImage\",\"enabled\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"149\"],\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"medium\",\"paddingBottom\":\"medium\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"378\":{\"type\":\"textWithImage\",\"enabled\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Learning by doing\",\"intro\":\"Layover with a Local is still a pilot. That\'s why the app is designed to learn from every experience.\",\"body\":\"When a meetup is finished, the app asks both the traveler and local for feedback. The app will be available starting in mid-March and the service is initially for travelers departing from the United States, Canada and Italy.\",\"image\":[\"379\"],\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"imagePosition\":\"left\",\"paddingTop\":\"medium\",\"paddingBottom\":\"none\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}}},\"41\":\"KLM Royal Dutch Airlines\",\"31\":{\"118\":{\"type\":\"item\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Development\",\"contributorName\":\"Superhero Cheesecake\"}}},\"40\":[\"121\"],\"75\":\"Visit website\",\"76\":\"https:\\/\\/layoverwithalocal.klm.com\\/\",\"50\":\"\",\"39\":\"Turn your transfer into a trip\",\"36\":\"\",\"83\":[\"390\"],\"43\":\"Mobile Application\",\"34\":{\"122\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Art direction\"}},\"123\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"UI design\"}},\"124\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Concept\"}},\"125\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Service design\"}},\"126\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Character design\"}},\"127\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Animation\"}},\"128\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"UX design\"}},\"129\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Strategy\"}}}}}', '2016-04-17 16:41:55', '2016-04-17 16:41:55', '03fad521-2800-4ebd-b5a1-be3cc9a1a2ab'),
