sive mini trip\",\"intro\":\"In collaboration with the national railway company we offer the traveler a free train ticket into the city.\",\"body\":\"But there is more. At selected bars, they can get their first drink for free, available through an in-app coupon. \",\"image\":[\"364\"],\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"imagePosition\":\"right\",\"paddingTop\":\"small\",\"paddingBottom\":\"small\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"147\":{\"type\":\"textTwoColumns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"So, how do we get the locals to sign up?\",\"intro\":\"We\\u2019re targeting locals that have an intrinsic motivation to meet up. Language students, for example, can practice their italian with a real italian. \",\"body\":\"In collaboration with language schools, the expat centre and local bars we make sure to find locals that are excited for a meetup. One lucky local will win a ticket to the country of the traveler.\",\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"medium\",\"paddingBottom\":\"medium\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"148\":{\"type\":\"largeImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"146\"],\"backgroundColor\":\"#cae3ed\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"medium\",\"paddingBottom\":\"medium\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"369\":{\"type\":\"largeImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"149\"],\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"medium\",\"paddingBottom\":\"medium\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"378\":{\"type\":\"textWithImage\",\"enabled\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Learning by doing\",\"intro\":\"Layover with a Local is still a pilot. That\'s why the app is designed to learn from every experience.\",\"body\":\"When a meetup is finished, the app asks both the traveler and local for feedback. The app will be available starting in mid-March and the service is initially for travelers departing from the Un