rs when attention is needed and has the driver all the information they need in a clear way that not only professional repairmen understand.\",\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"small\",\"paddingBottom\":\"small\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"448\":{\"type\":\"largeImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"450\"],\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"451\"],\"paddingTop\":\"small\",\"paddingBottom\":\"medium\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"185\":{\"type\":\"textTwoColumns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"An extension of the car\",\"intro\":\"From the beginning we knew we wanted to look for a balance where the app feels like an extension of the car as well as feel like a native mobile tool to manage all the information. \",\"body\":\"The dashboard is one of those places where most hints were taken from the real dashboard. Things such as the fuel gauge and the iconography on the keyfob were replicated to be used in the app.\",\"textColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#00b1eb\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"big\",\"paddingBottom\":\"none\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}},\"445\":{\"type\":\"largeImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"443\"],\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"588\"],\"paddingTop\":\"small\",\"paddingBottom\":\"medium\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}},\"210\":{\"type\":\"textWithImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"An extension of your car\",\"intro\":\"Besides basic information like fuel-level, brakes and doors, every possible part that can submit signals through your car\\u2019s computer is featured in the My Car section.\",\"body\":\"\",\"image\":[\"203\"],\"textColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#14222a\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"imagePosition\":\"left\",\"paddingTop\":\"small\",\"paddingBottom\":\"small\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}},\"211\":{\"type\":\"textWithImage\",\"enabled\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"The same information your mechanic gets\",\"intro\":\"Besides basic information like fuel-level, brakes and doors, every possible part that can submit signals through your car\\u2019s computer is featured in the My Car section.\",\"body\":\"\",\"image\":[\"209\"],\"textColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#14222a\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"imagePosition\":\"right\",\"paddingTop\":\"small\",\"paddingBottom\":\"small\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}},\"214\":{\"type\":\"textWithImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Three levels of warning signs.\",\"intro\":\"The app supports three statuslevels of a specific part. Good, warning and error. Depending on the level, the app gives you instructions on what to do next.\",\"body\":\"\",\"image\":[\"212\"],\"textColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#14222a\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"imagePosition\":\"left\",\"paddingTop\":\"small\",\"paddingBottom\":\"none\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}},\"216\":{\"type\":\"textTwoColumns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Monitoring your style of driving\",\"intro\":\"Think Blue is Volkswagen\\u2019s subbrand of responsible driving with care for the environment. With all data we can pull from your car, we can make a very accurate profile of your driving style. Your Think Blue score.\",\"body\":\"Based on this profile the app provides you with feedback on your driving and overall statistics on fuel consumption and progress in your style.\",\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#f0f5f8\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"medium\",\"paddingBottom\":\"small\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"440\":{\"type\":\"largeImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"438\"],\"backgroundColor\":\"#1cb2ec\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"585\"],\"paddingTop\":\"medium\",\"paddingBottom\":\"medium\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"220\":{\"type\":\"textTwoColumns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Keeping track of every drive you make\",\"intro\":\"Whenever you start driving, your trip is being automatically logged. Serving you with an overview of every trip you\\u2019ve made with your car.\",\"body\":\"With every trip that\\u2019s being logged, we register the start and end location, as well as the duration, fuel consumption, average speed and your ThinkBlue score. Besides that we\\u2019ll also allow drivers to mark a drive as commute, private or business for their administration.\",\"textColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#1cb2ec\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"small\",\"paddingBottom\":\"none\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"442\":{\"type\":\"largeImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"441\"],\"backgroundColor\":\"#1cb2ec\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"small\",\"paddingBottom\":\"medium\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"225\":{\"type\":\"textWithImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Dude, where\'s my car?\",\"intro\":\"No more searching for your car in an overcrowded parking lot with the car locator. \",\"body\":\"The car locator also comes with a movement alert. The app will notify you when your car starts moving, either because it\\u2019s being stolen, towed or when your son-in-law decides to take a joyride. \",\"image\":[\"222\"],\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#f0f5f8\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"imagePosition\":\"right\",\"paddingTop\":\"medium\",\"paddingBottom\":\"small\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"226\":{\"type\":\"textWithImage\",\"enabled\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Houston, we have a problem\",\"intro\":\"And whenever you may find yourself stuck alongside the road due to a breakdown, Volkswagen will come and get you. And because you\\u2019re using the app, they know exactly where you are and what\\u2019s wrong.\",\"body\":\"\",\"image\":[\"223\"],\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#f0f5f8\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"imagePosition\":\"left\",\"paddingTop\":\"none\",\"paddingBottom\":\"medium\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}}},\"41\":\"Volkswagen\",\"31\":{\"170\":{\"type\":\"item\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Development\",\"contributorName\":\"Sioux\"}}},\"40\":[\"161\"],\"75\":\"Download the app\",\"76\":\"\",\"50\":[\"435\"],\"39\":\"Control your car from the palm of your hand\",\"36\":\"\",\"83\":[\"436\"],\"43\":\"Mobile app\",\"34\":{\"171\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Concept\"}},\"172\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"UX Design\"}},\"173\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Art Direction\"}},\"174\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Visual Design\"}}}}}', '2016-04-20 10:21:34', '2016-04-20 10:21:34', '43c0dd75-6171-4c8e-9804-b2a1afd8f1f4'),
 ('631', '188', '3', '109', 'en_us', '75', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"109\",\"title\":\"Philips Brush Busters\",\"slug\":\"philips-brush-busters\",\"postDate\":1459955520,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"3\":{\"201\":{\"type\":\"textFullWidth\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"body\":\"Kids don\\u2019t like brushing their teeth. When Philips asked us to get kids to brush better, we knew we had to start with making brushing more fun. \",\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"big\",\"paddingBottom\":\"small\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"566\":{\"type\":\"largeImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"567\"],\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"565\"],\"paddingTop\":\"none\",\"paddingBottom\":\"none\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"206\":{\"type\":\"textTwoColumns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"How did it work\",\"intro\":\"We introduced Bj\\u00f8rn & Vicky, two characters with severe dental problems. And we asked kids to help them out using their connected toothbrushes.\",\"body\":\"\",\"textColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#86c0d3\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"medium\",\"paddingBottom\":\"medium\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}},\"550\":{\"type\":\"largeImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"553\"],\"backgroundColor\":\"#86c0d3\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"none\",\"paddingBottom\":\"none\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}},\"227\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"coverImage\":[\"563\"],\"vimeoId\":\"140226862\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"medium\",\"paddingBottom\":\"medium\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}},\"239\":{\"type\":\"largeImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"244\"],\"backgroundColor\":\"#f5f5f5\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"medium\",\"paddingBottom\":\"none\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"240\":{\"type\":\"textTwoColumns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Turning brushing into gaming\",\"intro\":\"To get kids brushing their full minutes every day we rewarded them with achievements and badges.\",\"body\":\"Every day they brushed perfectly, they would bring back a tooth of their favourite character. On top of that they could also collect badges for special achievements.\",\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#f5f5f5\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"medium\",\"paddingBottom\":\"big\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"247\":{\"type\":\"imageFull\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"569\"],\"paddingTop\":\"none\",\"paddingBottom\":\"none\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}},\"248\":{\"type\":\"imageGallery\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"602\",\"603\",\"604\",\"605\"],\"backgroundColor\":\"#4e4e4e\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"medium\",\"paddingBottom\":\"medium\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}},\"391\":{\"type\":\"textTwoColumns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"From app to ecosystem\",\"intro\":\"Brush Busters is the start of an ecosystem that connects kids, parents and the dentist.\",\"body\":\"In the app, parents can set rewards connected to brushing behaviour. And the dentist can give kids advice on where to brush better.\",\"textColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#83a9da\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"medium\",\"paddingBottom\":\"none\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}},\"571\":{\"type\":\"largeImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"570\"],\"backgroundColor\":\"#83a9da\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"none\",\"paddingBottom\":\"none\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}}},\"41\":\"Philips\",\"31\":{\"189\":{\"type\":\"item\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Development\",\"contributorName\":\"Superhero Cheesecake \"}},\"190\":{\"type\":\"item\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"3D and Animation\",\"contributorName\":\"Colorbleed\"}},\"191\":{\"type\":\"item\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Sound\",\"contributorName\":\"Big Orange\"}}},\"40\":[\"583\"],\"75\":\"Download app\",\"76\":\"inionii\",\"50\":\"\",\"39\":\"Making brushing more fun\",\"36\":{\"574\":{\"type\":\"honour\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"honourName\":\"3 x Spinawards\",\"logo\":[\"430\"]}},\"578\":{\"type\":\"honour\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"honourName\":\"2 X ADCN \",\"logo\":[\"576\"]}},\"579\":{\"type\":\"honour\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"honourName\":\"Red Dot Awards\",\"logo\":[\"577\"]}},\"580\":{\"type\":\"honour\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"honourName\":\"Mobile of the day\",\"logo\":[\"32\"]}}},\"83\":[\"581\"],\"43\":\"Mobile app\",\"34\":{\"192\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Interaction design\"}},\"193\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"UX design\"}},\"194\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Creative direction\"}},\"195\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Concept\"}},\"196\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Strategy\"}}}}}', '2016-04-20 13:20:13', '2016-04-20 13:20:13', '091a9987-f04f-4d1c-8657-b07adb4034e7'),
 ('632', '117', '3', '109', 'en_us', '75', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"109\",\"title\":\"Layover with a Local\",\"slug\":\"layover-with-a-local\",\"postDate\":1458311040,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"3\":{\"130\":{\"type\":\"textFullWidth\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"body\":\"KLM Layover with a Local turns transfers into trips. It\'s connecting the travelers with a stop in Amsterdam airport the opportunity to meet up with a local and get a taste of Amsterdam.\",\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"big\",\"paddingBottom\":\"big\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"132\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"coverImage\":[\"584\"],\"vimeoId\":\"161207812\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"none\",\"paddingBottom\":\"small\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"134\":{\"type\":\"textWithImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"70% of travelers have a layover in Amsterdam\",\"intro\":\"With Amsterdam Central Station just 15 minutes away, why not make use of it? Adventure is just around the corner. \",\"body\":\"With Amsterdam Central Station just 15 minutes away, why not make use of it? Adventure is just around the corner. \",\"image\":[\"362\"],\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"imagePosition\":\"left\",\"paddingTop\":\"big\",\"paddingBottom\":\"small\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"136\":{\"type\":\"textWithImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"A match made in heaven\",\"intro\":\"At the heart of the app is a smart matchmaking mechanism that matches travelers to locals.\",\"body\":\"Using their social profile, interests, shared languages and availability we made sure they would hit it off right away. \",\"image\":[\"135\"],\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"imagePosition\":\"right\",\"paddingTop\":\"big\",\"paddingBottom\":\"big\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"137\":{\"type\":\"textTwoColumns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"A personal layover guide for travelers\",\"intro\":\"Leaving the airport during a layover is potentially stressful. That\\u2019s why we created a personal layover guide that gives the traveler step-by-step directions.\",\"body\":\"The layover guide is made up from dynamic cards that offer relevant actions at the appropiate times. Real-time notifications ensure that the traveler returns to the airport in time.\",\"textColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#00a1de\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"big\",\"paddingBottom\":\"small\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}},\"376\":{\"type\":\"largeImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"375\"],\"backgroundColor\":\"#00a1de\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"none\",\"paddingBottom\":\"medium\",\"uiColor\":\"white\"}},\"143\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"coverImage\":[\"595\"],\"vimeoId\":\"157411018\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"big\",\"paddingBottom\":\"big\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"145\":{\"type\":\"textWithImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"An all-inclusive mini trip\",\"intro\":\"In collaboration with the national railway company we offer the traveler a free train ticket into the city.\",\"body\":\"But there is more. At selected bars, they can get their first drink for free, available through an in-app coupon. \",\"image\":[\"364\"],\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"imagePosition\":\"right\",\"paddingTop\":\"small\",\"paddingBottom\":\"small\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"147\":{\"type\":\"textTwoColumns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"So, how do we get the locals to sign up?\",\"intro\":\"We\\u2019re targeting locals that have an intrinsic motivation to meet up. Language students, for example, can practice their italian with a real italian. \",\"body\":\"In collaboration with language schools, the expat centre and local bars we make sure to find locals that are excited for a meetup. One lucky local will win a ticket to the country of the traveler.\",\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"medium\",\"paddingBottom\":\"medium\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"148\":{\"type\":\"largeImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"146\"],\"backgroundColor\":\"#cae3ed\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"medium\",\"paddingBottom\":\"medium\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"369\":{\"type\":\"largeImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"149\"],\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"medium\",\"paddingBottom\":\"medium\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"378\":{\"type\":\"textWithImage\",\"enabled\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Learning by doing\",\"intro\":\"Layover with a Local is still a pilot. That\'s why the app is designed to learn from every experience.\",\"body\":\"When a meetup is finished, the app asks both the traveler and local for feedback. The app will be available starting in mid-March and the service is initially for travelers departing from the United States, Canada and Italy.\",\"image\":[\"379\"],\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"imagePosition\":\"left\",\"paddingTop\":\"medium\",\"paddingBottom\":\"none\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}}},\"41\":\"KLM Royal Dutch Airlines\",\"31\":{\"118\":{\"type\":\"item\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Development\",\"contributorName\":\"Superhero Cheesecake\"}}},\"40\":[\"121\"],\"75\":\"Visit website\",\"76\":\"https:\\/\\/layoverwithalocal.klm.com\\/\",\"50\":\"\",\"39\":\"Turn your transfer into a trip\",\"36\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"honour\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"honourName\":\"Spinawards Gold\",\"logo\":[\"430\"]}}},\"83\":[\"390\"],\"43\":\"Mobile Application\",\"34\":{\"122\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Art direction\"}},\"123\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"UI design\"}},\"124\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Concept\"}},\"125\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Service design\"}},\"126\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Character design\"}},\"127\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Animation\"}},\"128\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"UX design\"}},\"129\":{\"type\":\"role\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"role\":\"Strategy\"}}}}}', '2016-04-22 09:45:23', '2016-04-22 09:45:23', '4fe561eb-6d59-49d5-8b0d-0e14286d24b7'),
