u start driving, your trip is being automatically logged. Serving you with an overview of every trip you\\u2019ve made with your car.\",\"body\":\"With every trip that\\u2019s being logged, we register the start and end location, as well as the duration, fuel consumption, average speed and your ThinkBlue score. Besides that we\\u2019ll also allow drivers to mark a drive as commute, private or business for their administration.\",\"textColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#1cb2ec\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"small\",\"paddingBottom\":\"none\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"442\":{\"type\":\"largeImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"441\"],\"backgroundColor\":\"#1cb2ec\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"paddingTop\":\"small\",\"paddingBottom\":\"medium\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"225\":{\"type\":\"textWithImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Dude, where\'s my car?\",\"intro\":\"No more searching for your car in an overcrowded parking lot with the car locator. \",\"body\":\"The car locator also comes with a movement alert. The app will notify you when your car starts moving, either because it\\u2019s being stolen, towed or when your son-in-law decides to take a joyride. \",\"image\":[\"222\"],\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#f0f5f8\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"imagePosition\":\"right\",\"paddingTop\":\"medium\",\"paddingBottom\":\"small\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}},\"226\":{\"type\":\"textWithImage\",\"enabled\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Houston, we have a problem\",\"intro\":\"And whenever you may find yourself stuck alongside the road due to a breakdown, Volkswagen will come and get you. And because you\\u2019re using the app, they know exactly where you are and what\\u2019s wrong.\",\"body\":\"\",\"image\":[\"223\"],\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#f0f5f8\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"imagePosition\":\"left\",\"paddingTop\":\"none\",\"paddingBottom\":\"medium\",\"uiColor\":\"black\"}}},\"41\":\"V