 ('13', '81', 'en_us', 'Designing for a beloved brand', 'When we were asked to design the brand portal for Chocomel we knew it was about chocolate love. A lot of loyal fans have a healthy obsession for this tasty chocolate drink.', 'Chocomel wanted to position themselves as an A-brand beverage along with the common soft drinks. Their previous image was more cozy and soft. The new image on the otherhand was to be more fashionable and exclusive.', '#ffffff', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, 'small', 'medium', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-16 15:28:59', '2016-04-29 19:51:53', 'fbb4c01a-dce6-40c8-b03b-2605d901d98b'),
 ('14', '83', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-16 15:33:25', '2016-04-29 19:51:53', '17b736ea-105e-4688-8b83-09574c1cad2e'),
 ('15', '86', 'en_us', 'The voice of chocomel lovers', 'Instead of Chocomel telling visitors how great Chocomel really is, we enabled the already big group of fans and let them speak for the brand.', 'In a mix of owned and shared content, the homepage is build up from quotes on twitter, fanphoto’s on instagram and video’s on youtube.', '#f0e9e4', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#391f10', NULL, NULL, 'none', 'big', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-16 15:46:55', '2016-04-29 19:51:53', '4502ba85-9b22-45c4-873e-a0ff7907b663'),
 ('16', '89', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Enjoying your Chocomel hot or cold?', 'Winter or summer, Chocomel can be consumed\r\nboth hot and cold. ', 'Depending on the season, we present the hero product in a warm mug or a cold glass. Since there is an ever lasting discussion on how Chocomel should be consumed, we gave users the option to switch.', '#392012', NULL, NULL, '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'big', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'white', NULL, NULL, '2016-03-16 15:54:54', '2016-04-29 19:51:53', '58ceab7e-d5da-4da7-8ca7-b5a17ee6751f'),
