 ('18', '91', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Showcasing an icon', 'In a colorful design, we showed visitors life-size photography of the iconic Chocomel pack paired with a hot mug or a cool glass.', 'The product pages have all the key information visitors want to know about their drink: nutritional information, ingrediënts, pack sizes and tell about the durable chocolate that is used in the drink.', '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'small', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, '2016-03-16 16:47:03', '2016-04-29 19:51:53', 'c91180b6-0f74-4e9b-a673-126bc061460b'),
