 ('37', '177', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'My Volkswagen is a new connected car platform. Through this platform Volkswagen can build a stronger relationship between drivers, dealers and the brand, and develop different value added services for consumers and businesses.', '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, 'big', 'medium', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, '2016-04-06 14:48:55', '2016-04-29 19:40:20', 'd91e2c1f-f44c-474a-bcbc-6de862a61432'),
 ('38', '178', 'en_us', 'Connect with your car', 'The ‘Connected Car’ is an important development in automotive. A wealth of data about the vehicle can be unlocked and enriched with external data. ', 'This provides new opportunities for interaction with the car. Through a smartphone/tablet app, an online platform or other connected devices.', '#ffffff', 'right', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, 'medium', 'medium', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-04-06 14:48:55', '2016-04-29 19:40:20', '285ccd0e-3459-4aff-9736-11fe65922d74'),
 ('42', '185', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'An extension of the car', 'We felt a strong belief that the design of the My Volkswagen platform should present itself through sheer simplicity. \r\n', 'The app feels like a natural extension of your car and gives you the information you need – when you need it. This way we create a level playing field between you and the garage and signals upcoming maintenance in time, to prevent unnecessary repair costs or sudden breakdown.\r\n', '#00b1eb', NULL, NULL, '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'big', 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'white', NULL, NULL, '2016-04-06 15:09:14', '2016-04-29 19:40:20', '5d635d46-874a-483f-88c5-4023e1a5a50b'),
 ('43', '197', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Opening the black box', 'For most people, the technology inside a car is a complete black box. This creates an uncomfortable feeling of dependency from the car’s technology and from the garage or dealer.\r\n', 'The My Volkswagen app opens up all the data the car has available to it’s drivers. Giving them more control and insight. ', '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'small', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, '2016-04-06 15:14:17', '2016-04-29 19:40:20', 'ed20189b-f81a-4fe1-9b61-842ba0e5a7dd'),
 ('46', '201', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Kids don’t like brushing their teeth. When Philips asked us to get kids to brush better, we knew we had to start with making brushing more fun. ', '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, 'big', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, '2016-04-06 15:24:06', '2016-04-29 19:50:37', '85e9907b-4819-4f30-9b49-ed3d3507f271'),
 ('48', '206', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'How did it work', 'We introduced Bjørn & Vicky, two characters with severe dental problems. And we asked kids to help them out using their connected toothbrushes.', '', '#86c0d3', NULL, NULL, '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'medium', 'medium', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'white', NULL, NULL, '2016-04-06 15:30:59', '2016-04-29 19:50:37', '88b46e78-5f3f-46a9-96e7-ec70d1c07b85'),
 ('50', '210', 'en_us', 'Recognizable iconography', 'We have re-created all dashboard light icons in order to maintain consistency in between in-car messages and in-app status.', '', '#14222a', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, 'small', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'white', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-04-06 15:34:15', '2016-04-29 19:40:20', 'c1642f96-bafa-4b60-83c4-c0244558e6dc'),
 ('51', '211', 'en_us', 'Three levels of notification signs', 'The app supports three urgency levels of a specific notification: good, warning and error. ', 'Depending on the urgency, the app gives you instructions on what to do next.', '#14222a', 'right', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, 'small', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'white', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-04-06 15:34:15', '2016-04-29 19:40:20', '71d6419b-b465-4c8f-9fcc-5af8125d6bb8'),
 ('52', '214', 'en_us', 'Three levels of notification signs', 'The app supports three urgency levels of a specific notification: good, warning and error. ', 'Depending on the urgency, the app gives you instructions on what to do next.', '#14222a', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, 'small', 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'white', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-04-06 15:39:34', '2016-04-29 19:40:20', '15b30138-9af2-4249-a5e5-e21673c2b9e4'),
 ('53', '216', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Smarter driving with Think Blue', 'Next to tracking the car, the platform also tracks your driving behavior in terms of efficient driving.', 'We measure acceleration, breaking, corners and speed, and translate this to one uniform score that drivers can compare. We called this the ‘Think Blue score’, in line with Volkswagen’s Think Blue sustainability program.', '#f0f5f8', NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'medium', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, '2016-04-06 15:46:28', '2016-04-29 19:40:20', '79773c0e-2830-457e-9761-7b4a7285d8a7'),
 ('55', '220', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Keep track of every drive you make', 'Whenever you start driving, your trip is being automatically logged.', 'We serve you with an overview of every trip you’ve made with your car, so you can create a simple drive overview that you can use for your tax and administration. This data is also available in a portal for lease companies and mobility managers. \r\n', '#1cb2ec', NULL, NULL, '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'small', 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, '2016-04-06 15:54:53', '2016-04-29 19:40:20', '90b37fbb-2bd9-4ab3-9498-256ea4ac34e6'),
 ('57', '225', 'en_us', 'Dude, where\'s my car?', 'A third set of very simple, practical features was based on data that is relevant before or after a drive. ', 'Using the connected car’s track and trace functionalities, you always know where your car is, if it is locked and if you need to fill the tank.', '#f0f5f8', 'right', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, 'medium', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-04-06 16:12:17', '2016-04-29 19:40:20', 'be7622ad-a9c1-464a-bf46-697c64384b69'),
 ('58', '226', 'en_us', 'Houston, we have a problem', 'And whenever you may find yourself stuck alongside the road due to a breakdown, Volkswagen will come and get you. And because you’re using the app, they know exactly where you are and what’s wrong.', '', '#f0f5f8', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, 'none', 'medium', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-04-06 16:12:17', '2016-04-29 19:40:20', '3b90cdca-8025-4704-a454-212c026c4e90'),
 ('59', '227', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'medium', 'medium', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'white', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '140226862', '2016-04-07 09:51:01', '2016-04-29 19:50:37', 'd07fd571-cd09-4f32-849a-1efcfc361108'),
